OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FITV Border will be sitting down with
OL,7,Fall the main political party leaders
OL,8,Fduring the Holyrood election campaign.
OL,10,FThe fifth interview was with the
OL,11,FScottish Liberal Democrats' Alex Cole-
OL,12,FHamilton. Here are three things we
OL,13,Flearned.
OL,15,FNorth vs South
OL,17,FThe Scottish Liberal Democrats have
OL,18,Ften target constituencies at this
OL,19,Felection.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FSix of those are in the Highlands and/
OL,7,For islands. Three are in Edinburgh or
OL,8,FGlasgow suburbia. One is the party's
OL,9,FNorth Korean-like stronghold of Fife
OL,10,FNorth East. None are in the south of
OL,11,FScotland.
OL,13,FThat might surprise people who
OL,14,Fremember the not-too-distant days when
OL,15,Fthe Lib Dems counted the Scottish
OL,16,FBorders as a fiefdom for the party.
OL,18,FMr Cole-Hamilton rejects the
OL,19,Fsuggestion that he is excluding the
OL,20,Fsouth while he looks north for success
OL,21,Fat the election.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
