OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FHis party's manifesto promises new
OL,7,Fdedicated mental health beds for
OL,8,Fchildren and young people north of
OL,9,FDundee but nothing for the south.
OL,11,FThis is despite, like the north of
OL,12,FScotland, there being no beds in our
OL,13,Fregion.
OL,15,FThere have also been tragic examples
OL,16,Fof when care has failed, particularly
OL,17,Fwhen young people are inappropriately
OL,18,Fplaced in adult wards.
OL,20,FSo why is the pledge only for the
OL,21,Fnorth?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FMr Cole-Hamilton said: "I don't want
OL,7,Fto say that we're going to magic those
OL,8,Fbeds up overnight but it's wholly
OL,9,Finappropriate for young people, facing
OL,10,Fsome of the most vulnerable moments of
OL,11,Ftheir life, to be housed alongside
OL,12,Fadults. That shouldn't happen at all.
OL,14,F"So, it comes with a review of all
OL,15,Fremote and rural healthcare offers
OL,16,Fthat the SNP, I think, have neglected
OL,17,Frural Scotland particularly in the
OL,18,Fsouth and we need to make sure that
OL,19,Fthat need is addressed.
OL,26,@nD@XOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,F"And if that is dedicated beds then
OL,7,Fabsolutely we're committed to that.
OL,8,FBut I don't want to say to your
OL,9,Fviewers that's going to happen
OL,10,Fovernight."
OL,12,FAlso not happening overnight under the
OL,13,FLib Dem plans is an upgrade of the A75.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/15
