OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FAlthough Mr Cole-Hamilton said he
OL,7,Fwould want a full business case for
OL,8,Fdualling the road to be put forward
OL,9,Fwithin the first 100 days of the new
OL,10,Fparliament, it was the last route
OL,11,Fmentioned in his manifesto and there's
OL,12,Fno firm commitment on scope or
OL,13,Ftimetable for the work itself.
OL,15,FHe said: "I would want to make big
OL,16,Fstrides towards that by the end of
OL,17,Fthis parliament and if possible
OL,18,Fcomplete it.
OL,26,@wD@JOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,F"The thing about Lib Dems is that we
OL,7,Fdon't make false promises or promises
OL,8,Fwe can't keep." (note to readers:
OL,9,Fwe'll come back to this statement.)
OL,11,FWhat then about the Borders Railway?
OL,12,FIt was a Lib Dem achievement in
OL,13,Fgovernment to push through the
OL,14,Foriginal plans but again the manifesto
OL,15,Fonly pledges to look at a "potential
OL,16,Fextension" to the route.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@OO]pD@QpmqD@cpnwD@[OUxD@JO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FMr Cole-Hamilton said: "The Lib Dems
OL,7,Fdelivered the Borders Railway, we
OL,8,Fbrought the legislation through the
OL,9,Fparliament, and we would be committed
OL,10,Fto extending that when the time is
OL,11,Fright, when the money is there, but
OL,12,Fwe're not going to lead people up a
OL,13,Fgarden path and tell them we're going
OL,14,Fto do something tomorrow."
OL,16,FHe's not desperate to do a deal with
OL,17,FLabour. Honest!
OL,26,@nD@XOUvD@ZO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FIt is an open secret at Holyrood that
OL,7,FMr Cole-Hamilton ` at one point at
OL,8,Fleast ` fancied himself as Deputy
OL,9,FFirst Minister in an Anas Sarwar-led
OL,10,FLabour Scottish Government.
OL,12,FAnd none of the ten Lib Dem target
OL,13,Fconstituencies are in areas being
OL,14,Fseriously contested by their rivals in
OL,15,Fred.
OL,17,FSo does he still want Mr Sarwar to be
OL,18,Ffirst minister? The exchange on this
OL,19,Fpoint wasn't exactly convincing.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FMr Cole-Hamilton: "No. Listen there
OL,7,Fare no pacts or alliances with Labour."
OL,9,FITV Border: "But surely he's your
OL,10,Fchoice because you don't want John
OL,11,FSwinney, you've said that. You've said
OL,12,Fyou don't want the Conservatives.
OL,13,FYou've said you don't want Reform. So
OL,14,Fit doesn't leave you many options,
OL,15,Fdoes it?"
OL,26,@nD@SOUoD@gO]qD@MOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
