OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FMr Cole-Hamilton: "I don't deny any of
OL,7,Fthat but at the same time we, I think,
OL,8,Fhave an obligation if we're looking
OL,9,Ffor change, and there's an opportunity
OL,10,Fto unseat the current government,
OL,11,Fwhich needs to happen, which shares
OL,12,Four values, that vision for change
OL,13,Fwith fairness at its heart, then we
OL,14,Fwill look at it."
OL,16,FExpect a shift in that rhetoric if
OL,17,Fit's useful to both opposition parties
OL,18,Fonce votes have been counted.
OL,20,FCampaigning by the beaches, hoping for
OL,21,Fthe peach vote...
OL,26,@nD@SOUvD@QO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/15
