OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FA little earlier in this blog I said I
OL,7,Fwould come back to Mr Cole-Hamilton's
OL,8,Fstatement that Lib Dems always keep
OL,9,Ftheir promises.
OL,11,FI did return to that later to raise
OL,12,Fthe party's most famous broken
OL,13,Fpromise: U-turning on a 2010 pledge to
OL,14,Fvote against any increase to
OL,15,Funiversity tuition fees in England and
OL,16,FWales.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FIt led to the Lib Dems haemorrhaging
OL,7,Fvotes and an apology from former
OL,8,FDeputy Prime Minister Nick Clegg as he
OL,9,Fpaid the electoral price for going
OL,10,Finto coalition with the Conservatives
OL,11,Facross the UK.
OL,13,FMr Cole-Hamilton says now that he was
OL,14,Fa youth worker when all of this
OL,15,Funfolded and that the Liberals are
OL,16,F"under new management" across the UK
OL,17,Fand in Scotland.
OL,19,FHe said: "I would have made different
OL,20,Fdecisions and I think we've owned our
OL,21,Fmistakes and I think we have recovered.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@VO]{D@JOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,F"We're under new management now. This
OL,7,Fis a really exciting offer of hope and
OL,8,Fchange with fairness at its heart,
OL,9,Fwhich people right across the south of
OL,10,FScotland can get on board with that
OL,11,Fsecond, peach coloured, regional
OL,12,Fballot."
OL,14,FThe focus on the regional list is one
OL,15,Fof the biggest shifts in the Lib Dem
OL,16,Fcampaign.
OL,18,FParty strategists say it means they
OL,19,Fcan once again aim to have
OL,20,Frepresentation in every part of the
OL,21,Fcountry.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@HO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
