PN,35115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777395953
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the Alex
OL,4,CCole-Hamilton leader interview
OL,6,FAnd it's no surprise that the shift
OL,7,Ffollowed the defection of Jamie Greene
OL,8,Ffrom the Conservatives given how
OL,9,Feffective the "Peach Vote Tory"
OL,10,Fcampaign was in the 2021 Holyrood
OL,11,Felection.
OL,13,FWe'll find out soon enough if the Lib
OL,14,FDem version will be as successful.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,26,@qD@OOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/15
